	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under Paullus, and distinguished himself in the battle of Pydna (Cic. Off. 1.37; Plut. Aem. 21.1-3; Cat. Mai. 20.6-8; cf. Val. Max. 3.2.16; Iustin. 33.2.1-4; Frontin. Str. 4.5.17). See D.- G. 5.160, no. 16." .
